        Selling in Tennyson 2026
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Tennyson's tight river bend, the Queensland Tennis Centre precinct and the Tennyson Reach apartments create one of Brisbane's smallest and most tightly held prestige markets. Here is what sellers need to know in 2026.
      </p>
